title: Jim Starlin's Cosmic Guard + Kid Kosmos GN
description:
This torrent contains some of Jim Starlin's work away from the mainstream.

This series was published in 2004 by Devil's Due publishing and Dynamite Entertainment. The torrent contains issues 1 - 6. There is allegedly an issue 0, but I was unable to locate a scan of it.

Also included in the torrent is the follow-up story Kid Kosmos - Kidnapped published by Dynamite Entertainment in 2006.

This is the kind of cosmic storyline you would expect from the mind and hand of Jim Starlin.

Thanks to the scanners and the original sources who shall remain nameless.

Please seed. Please enjoy.
